This skill is affected by the {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerIntelligence}Intelligence{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Characteristic}characteristic{/g}.
It represents knowledge about the nature of {g|Encyclopedia:Warp}warp{/g} entities and their twisted physical manifestations. May give access to new dialogue options.
languages.original_text:
Этот навык зависит от {g|Encyclopedia:Characteristic}характеристики{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerIntelligence}Интеллект{/g}.
Навык показывает, насколько хорошо персонаж осведомлен о мрачных сущностях {g|Encyclopedia:Warp}варпа{/g} и их искаженных проявлениях в реальном мире. Может дать доступ к новым диалоговым опциям.

languages.original_text: This skill represents knowledge about some of the most infamous {g|Encyclopedia:Warp}warp{/g} entities and their twisted physical manifestations. Includes an understanding of the energy of the warp, its interaction and interrelation with realspace and how its tides and eddies affect travel between the stars. It can also be used to disarm warp infused traps
